<div id="home">
    <section class="intro-section">
        <div class="container-fluid intro-area">
            <div class="row intro-row">
                <div class="col-6 offset-1 pl-0">
                    <div class="about-body container-fluid pl-0 pb-5 d-flex flex-column align-items-start justify-content-end">
                        <h1 class="pb-1">Marlo M. Carreon</h1>
                        <h3 class="pb-2">Full-stack web developer based out of Los Angeles. I enjoy backend coding,
                            coffee, and most things javascript.</h3>
                        <p class="mb-5 pb-5">I enjoy creating things for the internet. I was raised an avid gamer
                            thanks to my father. Some of my other interests include full-stack pancakes, home cooking,
                            Reddit, foreign beers, making music, and snowboarding. Someday, I would like to program my
                            own video game; but for now I'll keep cooking these stacks. </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-4 pr-0">
                    <div class="contact-body container-fluid pl-0 pb-5 d-flex align-items-end justify-content-end flex-column text-right">
                        <h2 class="pb-3">Contact Me</h2>
                        <div><a href="/message" class="black">Click here to leave a message</a></div>
                        <div>marloadriancarreon@gmail.com</div>
                        <div class="mt-0"><a href="https://github.com/mcarreon" target="__blank">GitHub</a></div>
                        <div class="mt-0 mb-5 pb-5"><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/carryon" target="__blank">LinkedIn</a></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="content-section">
        <div class="container-fluid content-area">
            <div class="row content-row">
                <div class="col-4 pl-0 mt-2 pt-3 offset-1">
                    <h2 class="mb-0">Projects</h2>
                    <p class="project-area-desc mt-2">These are 16 of my most recent projects. To visit them or their repos, click the links under the website or repo columns.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row data-table-row mt-1">
                <div class="col-10 pl-0 offset-1">
                    <table class="table table-sm table-striped table-responsive content-table">
                        <thead>
                            <tr>
                                <th class="w-12" scope="col">Date</th>
                                <th class="w-10" scope="col">Type</th>
                                <th class="w-15" scope="col">Website</th>
                                <th class="w-5" scope="col">Repo</th>
                                <th class="w-50 project-desc-col" scope="col">Description</th>
                                <th scope="col">Tags</th>

                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody class="pl-2 project-data">
                            {{#each projectData}}
                            <tr>
                                <th >{{project_creation_date}}</th>
                                <th>{{project_type}}</th>
                                <th>
                                    <a href="{{project_host}}"target="__blank">{{project_name}}</a>
                                </th>
                                <th>
                                    <a href="{{project_link}}" target="__blank">Link</a>
                                </th>
                                <th class="project-desc">{{project_desc}}</th>
                                <th>{{project_tags}}</th>
                            </tr>
                            {{/each}}
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row api-row mt-3">
                <div class="col-10 pl-0 offset-1">
                    <span>I've put together a small API package where you can get a full list of my projects. The basic route is:  <a href="/api/projects" target="__blank">/api/projects</a></span>. You can also search by project type or name by adding another parameter like this <a href="/api/projects/assignment">/api/projects/assignment</a>.  
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script src="/js/index.js"></script>